news.title: Explain regularisation of illegal residential colonies on pasture land: HC to Rajasthan govt
news.para: ​​In its petition, the Shri Rajasthan Gau Seva Samiti stated the state government had introduced a policy on December 27 last year to regularise encroachments on the pasture land or gochar, which are over 35 years old.

news.title: Mumbai: ED attaches Omkar group's flats at Worli worth Rs 330 crore
news.para: Earlier, the ED had arrested Babulal Varma and Kamal Kishor, managing director and chairman of the Omkar group, respectively, in the case along with Sachin Joshi, promoter of J M Joshi group.

news.title: Telangana government now eyeing housing board land for auctions
news.para: The state government is learnt to have asked the housing board to hand over certain land parcels owned by it to the Hyderabad Metropolitan Development Authority (HMDA) for holding auctions.
